    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a gem. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. Whether you're commuting to work or heading out on a weekend getaway, this car is totally ready to hit the road! It\u2019s been well-loved and is looking for a great new home. Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
