    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double VANOS variable valve timing. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a limited-slip differential. The chassis has been enhanced with rear subframe reinforcement and upgraded polyurethane bushings to sharpen turn-in and mitigate fatigue. While it displays the honest patina of a well-loved driver\u2019s car, the mechanical vitals are robust, offering a visceral 8,000 RPM redline and unparalleled steering feedback.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
