    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This vehicle has been exceptionally well-cared for and presents beautifully. The exterior maintains a brilliant luster, with only minor, age-appropriate road nicks on the lower front fascia that do not detract from its overall presence. Inside, the cabin is a pristine, smoke-free environment; the premium upholstery is firm and free of any cracks or thinning, while the high-touch surfaces like the steering wheel and gear shift show minimal wear. Mechanically, the car is robust, featuring a documented service history with recent fluid changes and a fresh set of performance tires. The engine idles quietly and pulls strongly through all gears, providing a confident and smooth driving experience. All electronics, from the dual-zone climate control to the infotainment system, function perfectly. This is a turn-key vehicle that has been garage-kept and is ready for immediate enjoyment.",
      "price": 36800.0,
